iBut now there is a KernelSU Fork		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
hKernelSU-Next	URL:https://github.com/rifsxd/KernelSU-Next	{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
ithat supports both GKI and non-GKI kernels, so we can use it for the		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
ilatest features:		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
